Company Overview of PT. Vantage Drilling Company Indonesia



Snapshot People




Company Overview
PT. Vantage Drilling Company Indonesia is based in Jakarta, Indonesia. PT. Vantage Drilling Company Indonesia operates as a subsidiary of Vantage Drilling Company. 


Graha Mampang Building, 5th Floor, Jl. MampanNG Prpatan Raya 100, Kecamatan PancoranJakarta,  12760Indonesia



Phone: 62 281 404 4700








