 PT LINS Petrotama Energi  +  Onshore & Offshore  +  International Drilling  +  Energy Services  +  PROVIDE QUALITY SERVICES THAT MEET OUR CLIENTS NEEDS 








Drilling Unit
Operates a versatile fleet of 64 units that comprises drillships, jack-up rigs, semi-submersible rigs and tender rigs for operations in shallow to ultra-deepwater areas in harsh and benign environments.



Labour Supply
PT Lins has a diverse talent pool that have more than 10 years work of industry experience under their belts.
.



Maintenance & Catering
Offers variation menu of catering and support services, from food services to housekeeping and maintenance as comfortable as possible. 


Rig Management
We provide rig management specialist with personnel who are well experience and completed safety training.

 




Company Overview
PT. Lins Petrotama Energi (PT. LINS) is a Jakarta based, Indonesian registered company in the business of providing onshore and offshore international drilling and energy services.Our primary resource is highly qualified and experienced personnel, offering clients a blend of extensive practical knowledge with strong technical and logistical support. PT. LINS has a broad skill base made up of multi-disciplined operations/engineers, logistics specialists and contract/procurement personnel. Building on the knowledge and experience of our personnel, along with the commitment to utilize the most up to-date technology, enables PT. LINS to provide cost effective services to clients. Irrespective of the size of the work, PT. LINS offers a rapid understanding of the customer’s needs and a ability to provide added value and simple solutions to complex problems. . 

Our History

 Our People

To be the leading provider of international drilling quality and energy services by maximizing customer satisfaction through anticipating the customer’s equipment and operational needs and providing superior operational results.

 Our Strategy

To provide international drilling quality and energy services by offering our customers and associates the highest competitive standard of personnel, equipment and operational performance with emphasizing safety, healthy, environmental standard and business ethics.

 Our Principal

We are agents for the following distinguished international principals:


SEADRILL Management (S) Pte Ltd
ScanSeis Consulting Group AS

 Our Expertise



Labour supply for exploration. maintenance, production, and engineering projects
