 Who We Are 




 PT.  Accent  Jaya   Indonesia  company  established  in  2003  under  the  law  of Republic Indonesia is an  Marine  & Oilfield   Crew   Management   Services Company that   believes   in providing    quality services  to  all  its  clients with  experienced and safety  oriented   crew,  also   acts as   a   trade    field general in export,   import, local ,distributor ,supplier,   agent commissioner or   a   representative of the company domestic and foreign affairs,    real estate,     agriculture, consulting    services   for training and skills,management consulting services,  field of    labor, marketing, support crew services   for all type   of   vessel,  passenger ships  and mining,   which have  a long history  of cooperation with a various  clients  covering  Asia Pacific region and Middle East.  PT.  Accent  Jaya   Indonesia is one   of    the  fastest     growing    offshore  /  onshore Crew  Management Company providing Oil and Gas  Crew Services  to  Drilling  Rigs, Offshore Process Platforms, Engineering Maintenance, Working Barge, Cruise Ship, Yacht  and  Mining by request.Built    itself  a  reputation   of    providing   and   managing    experienced   and committed   crew to  all offshore  and  onshore   installations  due to constant upgrading of our  hiring system  and processing and training  of  our  employees   and our  focus  on  maintaining  international  quality standards.We  have been providing experienced and qualified personnel to all clients in the following categories and we are able to offer :DRILLING OIL & GAS : RIG MANAGER, TOOL PUSHER, TOUR PUSHER, DRILLER, ASSISTANT DRILLER, DERRICKMAN, PUMPMAN, MOTORMAN, FLOORMAN, ROUSTABOUT, PAINTER.CRANE OPERATOR, RADIO OPERATOR, STOREMAN, STOREKEEPER, WELDER, ELECTRICIAN, MECHANIC, MEDIC, SAFETY OFFICER/HSE, FIRE WATCH.MARINE :MASTER, CHIEF ENGINEER, CHIEF OFFICER, DECK OFFICER, BOSUN, AB, OILER, WIPER, CADET, STEWARD.CATERING :CHIEF COOK, ASSISTANT COOK, WESTERN COOK, STEWARD, GALLEY HAND, BAKER, MESS BOY, LAUNDRY, ROOM BOY.CRANE BARGE - ACCOMMODATION BARGE - FLOATING PRODUCTION STORAGE AND OFFLOADING - FLOATEL SUPERIOR, DREDGING SHIP, PLATFORM :BARGE MASTER, BARGE ENGINEER, FOREMAN RIGGER, RIGGER, WELDER, CRANE OPERATOR, ELECTRICIAN, MECHANIC, RADIO OPERATOR, SAFETY OFFICER/HSE, PIPE FITTER, PARAMEDIC, WELDER UNDERWATER, DIVING, FOREMAN SCAFFOLDING, SCAFFOLDER, PAINTER.PASSENGER SHIP - YACHT - CREW BOAT :DECK ENGINE RATING, COOK, ASSISTANT COOK, BAKER, STEWARD, ASSISTANT WAITER, CABIN STEWARD, LAUNDRY, ROOM BOY, AB,CADET.MINING By Request : WELDER, SENIOR CRANE OPERATOR, HELPER WELDER.We  recruit   the    crew   who   has   experience /  responsibility   with their position and having   al l required   document  based  on  the IMO  STANDARD,  IADC,ILO,  IWCF ,   DP 1.2. 3, STCW 1995/2010/2016, Etc.We  always follow  company  procedures and  rules and  we  work  hard and professional to fulfill the will of  our  principals.PT.   Accent   Jaya   Indonesia also  recruit  Drilling    and   Marine/Seafarers   also Mining   who are experience on :RIG SEMI SUBMERSIBLE, RIG JACKUP, LAND RIG, SWAMP RIG, MOBILE RIG, BARGE TENDER, PIPE LINE, PLATFORM, DRILL SHIP, FPSO, ACCOMMODATION CRANE BARGE, FLOATEL SUPERIOR, AHTS, PASSENGER SHIP, YACHT, FERRIES, TUG BOAT, TANKER, SUPPLY, CARGO, BULK CARRIERS, DREDGING SHIP, CREW BOAT/SUPPLY, MINING by Request. 












































