 Overview 




 Our    business    strategy     is    focused    on    providing    to   our   clients   with   a of   your  HR  department, extending  your company's  vision,  philosophies   and practices  to  our  crew,   We actively pursue  teamwork  with our clients, we proactively solve problems,  and  we   take  it  upon  ourselves to  listen  to  our principals in needs.  our business  is   managed   via   our   ISO   9001   Safety   and   Quality Management System (SQMS) with MLC 2006 (process)We  understand   the  drilling  and   marine  business,    Today,  it is  no  longer sufficient   to   remain   as passive participants.   Demand   by  the  principals  upon contractors  and  subcontractors  to  integrate their   safety  and  quality   management systems   are   now   routinely   specified  in  contracts.  We  are confident  that  we can meet your standards and expectations. PT.  Accent Jaya Indonesia   can  offer   more  than  just  qualified personnel,  we  take  care the crewing need such as :Selection and Recruitment.Payroll and General Administration.Training and Development.Competency Assurance.Safety Management + Accident Investigation.Performance Management.Human Logistics Worldwide. MissionThe Objective of ACCENT JAYA INDONESIA.PT is to develop and protect the interests of our principals, to meet profit expectations and to provide a secure and satisfying work environment between our Principals and Clients.To provide a complete and Professional Marine & Oilfield Service to our Clients.To comply with both Local and International Standard of safety and quality services.To provide the most qualified, hardworking, medically fit, honest, and highly skilled Indonesian workers.To meet and exceeds customers expectations.To provide full-time services for our Principals and Clients, in-terms of fairness and complete satisfaction in all aspect.Corporate VisionOur objective is to become the industry recognized premier supplier of skilled labour services within Asia Pacific and Middle East .We shall achieve our vision via the rigorous implementation and continuous improvements of our Safety and Quality Management System by integrating seamlessly our products and systems with the needs of our clients; and to continually assess our end-users’ requirements and satisfaction.In addition, our mission to enhance our client’s productivity by ensuring that our products and services meet their highest possible standards, with maximum cost effectiveness, lowest turnover and in the safest possible manner.  







































